=\"font-family:宋体\">联系人：</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吴满霞</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:21.0pt;\r\nline-height:23.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">联系电话：</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">0515-89803566&nbsp; 15950298580&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:21.0pt;\r\nline-height:23.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">地 &nbsp;址：盐城市钱江财富广场<span>A</span>座<span>4</span>楼</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'\"><span>&nbsp;</span></p>','','','','','');
