so-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;color:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">5</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";mso-hansi-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\r\ncolor:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;color:black;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">—10</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";color:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">月养老保险均在本单位缴纳。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\ncolor:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:1.5;layout-grid-mode:char;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\ncolor:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">4</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\"Times New Roman\";mso-hansi-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";color:black;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">、财务要求：投标人应具有独立订立合同的能力，未处于财产被接管、冻结和破产状态。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\ncolor:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:1.5;layout-grid-mode:char;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\ncolor:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">5</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\"Times New Roman\";mso-hansi-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";color:black;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">、本次招标不接受联合体投标。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;color:black;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\"></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:1.5;layout-grid-mode:char;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";mso-hansi-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\r\ncolor:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">三、投标保证金：本项目投标保证金数额为人民币</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\ncolor:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">2000</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\"Times New Roman\";mso-hansi-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";color:black;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">元整，具体详见招标文件。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;color:black;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\"></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:1.5;layout-grid-mode:char;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";mso-hansi-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\r\ncolor:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">四、评标办法：本项目采用</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;color:black;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">“</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n11.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";color:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">竞争性谈判</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\ncolor:black;mso-font-kernin