n:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:1.5;layout-grid-mode:\r\nchar;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5;color:black\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">、项目地点：盐城市毓龙西路</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;color:black\">166</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">号。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:1.5;layout-grid-mode:\r\nchar;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5;color:black\">3</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">、项目规模：新建停车综合楼，建筑面积约</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;color:black\">4.6</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">万㎡，设计地下</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;color:black\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">层，地上</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;color:black\">15</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">层，地下</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;color:black\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">万㎡，地上</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;color:black\">3.6</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">万㎡，其中车库面积</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;color:black\">2.4</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">万㎡，设置</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;color:black\">600</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">个停车位，新建投资约</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;color:black\">2.36</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">亿元。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:1.5;layout-grid-mode:\r\nchar;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5;color:black\">4</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">、招标范围：盐城市老年康复医院综合楼项目交通影响评价服务，编制交通影响报告。编制深度符合国家相关规范要求，并通过相关职能部门评审。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:1.5;layout-grid-mode:\r\nchar;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5;color:black\">5</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">、编制要求：交通影响评价编制的成果为交通影响评价报告，包括文本和图纸。建设项目规划设计方案报审阶段的交通影响评价报告内容应包括建设项目概况、评价范围与年限、建设项目周边交通现状及评价、建设项目周边相关规划、交通需求预测、交通影响程度评价、交通改善措施与评价、结论和建议等。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:1.5;layout-grid-mode:\r\nchar;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5;color:black\">6</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">、质量要求：满足国家及行业相关法律法规、标准规范要求，并确保通过招标人及相关行业主管部门技术的审核，并获得相应的批复。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:1.5;layout-grid-mode:\r\nchar;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">二、投标人须具备以下条件：</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:1.5;layout-grid-mode:\r\nchar;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5;color:black\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">、投标人资格要求：投标人须是在中国境内注册，具有城市规划编制甲级资质的独立法人。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:1.5;layout-grid-mode:\r\nchar;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5;color:black\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">、项目负责人为投标人本单位正式职工，须具有中级及以上职称证书。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:1.5;layout-grid-mode:\r\nchar;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5;color:black\">3</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">、投标人须确保授权委托人和项目负责人为本单位的正式职工，并确保从投标截止日当月向前连续</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;color:black\">6</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">个月均在本单位缴纳养老保险</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;color:black\">(</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">例：如开标日期为</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;color:black\">2021</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">年</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;color:black\">11</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">月</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;color:black\">**</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">日，则投标单位需保证以上人员</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;color:black\">2021</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">年</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;color:black\">5</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">月—</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;color:black\">10</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">月养老保险均在本单位缴纳。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:1.5;layout-grid-mode:\r\nchar;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5;color:black\">4</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">、财务要求：投标人应具有独立订立合同的能力，未处于财产被接管、冻结和破产状态。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:1.5;layout-grid-mode:\r\nchar;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5;color:black\">5</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">、本次招标不接受联合体投标。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:1.5;layout-grid-mode:\r\nchar;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">三、投标保证金</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;color:black\">:</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">本项目投标保证金数额为人民币</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;color:black\">2000</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">元整，具体详见招标文件。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:1.5;layout-grid-mode:\r\nchar;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">四、评标办法</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;color:black\">:</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">本项目采用“竞争性谈判”法，具体详见招标文件。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:1.5;layout-grid-mode:\r\nchar;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">五、招标文件领取：</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:1.5;layout-grid-mode:\r\nchar;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">投标报名及竞争性谈判文件的获取，请符合上述资质条件的投标人携带单位介绍信</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;color:black\">(</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">或授权委托书，须注明联系人、电话及邮箱</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;color:black\">)</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">原件到</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">江苏全盛工程造价事务所有限公司</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;color:black\">(</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">盐城市解放南路</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;color:black\">199</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">号阳光大厦</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;color:black\">B</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">座四楼</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;color:black\">)</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">投标报名，投标报名时间</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;color:black\">2021</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">年</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;color:black\">12</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">月</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;color:black\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">日</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;color:black\">