e\">、招投标监督管理机构及投诉电话：盐城市第一人民医院纪检监察室，联系电话<span lang=\"EN-US\">0515-66696810</span>。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.5pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:black\"></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt;\r\nmso-line-height-rule:exactly;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;background:white\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:black;background:white\">其余内容详见招标文件。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p>\r\n<p align=\"right\" style=\"text-align:right;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;background:\r\nwhite\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\ncolor:black;background:white\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"right\" style=\"text-align:right;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;background:\r\nwhite\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\ncolor:black;background:white\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:black;background:white\">招标人：盐城市第一人民医院<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p>\r\n<p align=\"right\" style=\"text-align:right;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;background:\r\nwhite;word-break:break-all\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n宋体;color:black;background:white\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:black;\r\nbackground:white\">时间：<span lang=\"EN-US\">2021</span>年<span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span>日<span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:yes\">&nbsp; </span></span></span></p>','','','','','');
INSERT INTO `p8_cms_item_article_addon` VALUES ('2332','3155','1','','','1、盐城市第一人民医院化粪池清理等项目，资金已落实，招标人盐城市第一人民医院现对该项目进行公开招标，诚邀潜在的投标人参加投标。2、项目概况与招标内容2.1项目名称：盐城市第一人民医院化粪池清理等项目。2.2项目地点：盐城市第一人民医院主院区（人民南路66号）、','172.16.100.2','172.16.100.2','1638841655','<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:21.0pt;\r\nbackground:white\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;\r\nbackground:white\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;background:\r\nwhite\">、盐城市第一人民医院化粪池清理等项目，资金已落实，招标人盐城市第一人民医院现对该项目进行公开招标，诚邀潜在的投标人参加投标。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:21.0pt;\r\nbackground:white\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;\r\nbackground:white\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;background:\r\nwhite\">、项目概况与招标内容</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:21.0pt;\r\nbackground:white\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;\r\nbackground:white\">2.1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;background:\r\nwhite\">项目名称：盐城市第一人民医院化粪池清理等项目。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:21.0pt;\r\nbackground:white\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;\r\nbackground:white\">2.2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;background:\r\nwhite\">项目地点：盐城市第一人民医院主院区（人民南路<span>66</span>号）、北区（毓龙西路<span>166</span>号）、五官科医院（南城河路<span>12</span>号）、儿童医院（毓龙西路<span>34</span>号）</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-seri